simple_means.memory_skill: gas 气体 + eous 有…性质的，关于…的 → 气体的

tr: existing as or having characteristics of a gas
example: steam is water is the gaseous state

value.def: You use gaseous to describe something which is in the form of a gas, rather than a solid or liquid.

example.ex: Freon exists both in liquid and gaseous states.
example.tran: 氟利昂有液态和气态两种形态。

rootsaffixes.indicate: 表形容词，“有…性质的，关于…的”
rootsaffixes.title: -eous, -ious, -ous, -tious, -uous
